com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class GetAggregatePeriodRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianRequest
      • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianObjectRequest
        • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.GetAggregatePeriodRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecordKeyProvider, SiperianObjectUidProvider, Serializable

    public class GetAggregatePeriodRequest
extends SiperianObjectRequest
implements RecordKeyProvider
    Represents a request object to retrieve the aggregate period for a base object record. Aggregate period is an aggregate of all the effective periods of a base object record and its cross-reference records that encompass the specified effective date.

    See Also:
    GetAggregatePeriodResponse, SiperianObjectRequest, Serialized Form

    API Pair: GetAggregatePeriodResponse
